But his revenue went up?


You'd think being the face of your YouTube channel is the only way to succeed, right?


Like most people, that's what Davis thought.


Every video meant hours in front of the camera. 


Recording. 


Re-recording. 


Trying to look perfect for his management consulting audience.

 
Download


Sure, he was making $20K a month, but at what cost?


Between running his business, serving clients, and creating content... Davis was drowning.


"I needed a better process


Something that could scale without stealing all my time."


That's when we showed him a different approach


Instead of being in every video, what if he could build a system that worked without him?


Not faceless automation. 


Not generic AI content.


But a true hybrid personal brand that could:


> Maintain his channel's authority

> Deliver high-value consulting advice

> Run smoothly without requiring his daily presence


After months of searching, Davis found a silver lining, and we immediately got to work.


He finally found the help he needed.


The results?


His channel leaped from $20K to $100K a month.


But thats just the beginning.


His viewers didn't just accept this new format, they loved it. 


Because the value and expertise remained consistent, even when Davis wasn't on camera.


"I can't say enough things about working with ShaneWe've 4X'd the number of leads coming in every single week compared to a year ago."


While other creators are still chained to their cameras, Davis built something bigger than himself.


That's the power of a hybrid personal brand.


It gives you room to grow beyond the limitations of being a one-person show.
